All they do is Investigate, as it turns out, crimes that they instigated & committed. The Mueller No Collusion decision wasn't even discussed-and she was a disaster at W.H.”
pageContext.analysis: Many of the bills passed so far in the House have been blocked by Republicans in the Senate. Two significant actions that passed in both Houses -- disapproving of Trump's declaration of an emergency to transfer wall funds and a resolution to end U.S. assistance in the war in Yemen -- were vetoed by Trump.
